[[File:Galaxies_Opera_House_Posters.jpg|thumb|300px|Signs for ''Jedi on the Roof'' and other shows outside the Galaxies Opera House]]
'''''Jedi on the Roof''''' was a musical playing at the [[Galaxies Opera House/Legends|Galaxies Opera House]] in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]]. A sign advertising the show was displayed outside of the [[Opera/Legends|opera]] house during a performance of [[Squid Lake/Legends|''Squid Lake'']] attended by [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]]. The sign depicted a silhouette of the [[Jedi Order/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Master]] [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] holding [[Gender/Legends|his]] [[Yoda's lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]].<ref name="Revenge of the Clone Menace">''[[Tag & Bink: Revenge of the Clone Menace]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
This title has a real-world parallel to the musical [[Wikipedia:Fiddler on the Roof|''Fiddler on the Roof'']].

